How to Identify a Lie
A look at the recent headlines indicates the extent to which deception and lies are omnipresent in daily life.
The Republican candidate for President Herman Cain is busy exchanging allegations of sexual harassment with several women; each side accuses the other of lying.
Penn State administrators were accused of having allegedly covered reports that a retired football coach sexually assaulted boys.
